Description: 
    A toolbox for conducting reproducible psychometric experiments to explore 
    how structural modifications in item-based measurements affect outcome 
    metrics. The core function 'dropit()' systematically removes items from 
    questionnaire data to examine their impact on Cronbach’s alpha or 
    confirmatory factor analysis (CFA) loadings. All procedures are fully 
    traceable, with strict input validation, detailed message handling, and 
    informative console output to support transparent and iterative research 
    workflows.
